sequenceDiagram
    actor H as Human
    participant I as /idea
    participant CP as /create-project
    participant Reg as ~/.claude/registry.md
    participant FS as ~/.claude/ideas/

    H->>I: pitch idea (or informal "what if we..." language)

    note over I: Capture
    I->>Reg: Assign IDEA-NNN
    I->>H: Restate idea — confirm understanding

    note over I: Grill (one question at a time, AI recommends each answer)
    loop Problem → Baseline Measurements → Destination Targets → Journey
        I->>H: Question + recommended answer + challenge
        H->>I: Answer
    end

    I->>H: Draft journey diagram (mid-grill, before complete)
    H->>I: Feedback on diagram

    I->>H: Impact vs Effort 2×2 — confirm position
    H->>I: Confirm

    I->>H: Feature estimate (AI token cost band + story points)
    H->>I: Confirm estimates

    note over I: Decision gate
    I->>H: ACCEPT / DECLINE / HOLD

    alt ACCEPT
        I->>FS: Save idea.md + diagram.mmd + diagram-v1-idea.mmd
        I->>Reg: Update registry (Active, IDEA-NNN)
        I->>H: Suggest /create-project
        H->>CP: /create-project
        CP->>Pref: Read preferences.md (platform, username)
        CP->>Reg: Assign PROJ-NNN
        CP->>H: Confirm repo name + visibility — type CONFIRM
        H->>CP: CONFIRM
        CP->>FS: Scaffold Forge template + generate README.md
        CP->>FS: git init → initial commit
        CP->>FS: Create remote repo + push (gh/glab/bb or manual steps)
        CP->>Reg: Update registry (PROJ-NNN ↔ IDEA-NNN cross-ref)
        CP->>FS: Update CLAUDE.md + idea.md with cross-refs
        CP->>H: Suggest /grill-with-docs + priority ranking + sprint/PI assignment
    else HOLD
        I->>FS: Save idea.md (status: Holding)
        I->>Reg: Update registry (Holding)
    else DECLINE
        I->>FS: Archive idea.md + reason
        I->>Reg: Update registry (Declined)
    end
